<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qscissortest.xml">QScissorTest</db:link> class enables scissor test, which discards fragments outside the rectangular area of the screen specified by the left, bottom, width and height properties.</db:para>
</db:section>
